    <h1>Introduction to MERN Stack</h1>

    <p>The MERN stack is a popular set of technologies used for building full-stack web applications. It includes MongoDB for the database, Express.js as the backend web framework, React for building user interfaces, and Node.js as the server runtime environment.</p>

    <ol>
        <li>MongoDB</li>
        <li>Express.js</li>
        <li>React</li>
        <li>Node.js</li>
    </ol>

